     "6903fcf1-26eb-43cb-9c11-0656f176ec5e"], Cell[
    "the depth of the circuit: the number of gate layers", "TableText",
     ExpressionUUID->"7705fc41-7300-4f31-b51b-b4d0e40b6243"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "b805e92b-3b08-4f25-9a56-94b4e09381be"], Cell[TextData[{
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<OperatorCount\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "49b32305-d1f6-4ad6-8928-fe74a7ed6fa5"],
     " or ",
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<GateCount\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "7d40232f-d4d2-4d09-9c82-1179115fe3f2"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"0b120583-f093-4dd7-8906-b72178c481e3"], 
    Cell["the total number of operators (gates) in the circuit", "TableText",
     ExpressionUUID->"ab53b427-4e74-48a1-ad63-5d2fb258fc77"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "264edc7b-7237-42e1-ae47-2423f77dd598"], Cell[TextData[{
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<InputDimensions\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "34943bc9-19b7-43aa-a067-49e19fbec6bb"],
     " / ",
     Cell[
     BoxData["\"\<OutputDimensions\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
      "e7aa0915-87b1-46a1-85ad-b9b8d46b3190"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"3f990e90-5aea-40f2-9f7a-9d36a6d80e20"], 
    Cell["the list of input / output qudit dimensions of the circuit", 
     "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"bceda728-eefa-4e58-9842-d3a0025c2cd8"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "e2d11099-f883-4d84-a1e8-54245451e206"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
    BoxData["\"\<Operators\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
     "3458ed87-c629-4162-bc05-c61a2b76d89d"]], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "d68f0fa5-fea2-4b9b-9dca-bbf82a3b1099"], Cell[
    "the list of operators (gates) in the circuit", "TableText",
     ExpressionUUID->"e7905fc6-43f2-430a-8d8b-1e548dad31b1"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "057d0785-62df-4ee0-bcba-8270473c2fa8"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
