     "07eed137-9bcb-4728-8749-af8e4165dbfa"], Cell["\<\
the circuit operator: the single quantum operator representing the overall \
transformation done by the circuit\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"8fe8fd10-6e1a-448a-9b2a-935ae4787d81"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "d96064f7-beeb-457a-bdb0-34738487cec8"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
