     "245d27b4-2bf5-46d9-b78a-761b5cfb10cc"], Cell["\<\
the list of orders (input/output qudits) of the operators in the circuit\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"be2c8e32-8b0d-4d15-9a38-82d6eb5c3e6e"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
