the picture of the circuit (e.g. Schrodinger, Heisenberg or PhaseSpace)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"91c4ac25-2779-429d-a1c2-4d53f6ad0fe3"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "060377b6-5740-4354-9ce1-81e9a4145808"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
